        <item>
            <title>【評測】Bandai Hi-Metal R 超時空要塞 Macross 7 VF-19 改　更小比例完全變形</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/07/%e3%80%90%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac%e3%80%91bandai-hi-metal-r-%e8%b6%85%e6%99%82%e7%a9%ba%e8%a6%81%e5%a1%9e-macross-7-vf-19%e6%94%b9%e3%80%80%e6%9b%b4%e5%b0%8f%e6%af%94%e4%be%8b%e5%ae%8c%e5%85%a8%e8%ae%8a/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%25a9%2595%25e6%25b8%25ac%25e3%2580%2591bandai-hi-metal-r-%25e8%25b6%2585%25e6%2599%2582%25e7%25a9%25ba%25e8%25a6%2581%25e5%25a1%259e-macross-7-vf-19%25e6%2594%25b9%25e3%2580%2580%25e6%259b%25b4%25e5%25b0%258f%25e6%25af%2594%25e4%25be%258b%25e5%25ae%258c%25e5%2585%25a8%25e8%25ae%258a</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/07/%e3%80%90%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac%e3%80%91bandai-hi-metal-r-%e8%b6%85%e6%99%82%e7%a9%ba%e8%a6%81%e5%a1%9e-macross-7-vf-19%e6%94%b9%e3%80%80%e6%9b%b4%e5%b0%8f%e6%af%94%e4%be%8b%e5%ae%8c%e5%85%a8%e8%ae%8a/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 04:30:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1261441</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日愈來愈多超時空要塞的 Figure 及模型推出，Bandai 的 HI-METAL R 系列，也推出了《超時空要塞 7》的 VF-19 改，由主角巴沙拿駕駛，亦是 Fire Bomber 樂隊的歌手。</p><p><a title="_DSC0520" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975028761/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975028761_2d6874472d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0520" width="877" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>今次的 VF-19 改包裝盒設計相當貼心，背後設有一個小天窗，讓你能夠直接看到內部的內容物，這種設計在 Hi-METALR 系列中頗為常見。值得要讚讚的是，地台上採用了 Fire Bomber 的金色燙金製作字體，效果非常靚仔。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261443" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0505-694x559.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="559" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0505-694x559.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0505-scaled.jpg 1117w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261444" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0506-694x538.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="538" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0506-694x538.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0506-scaled.jpg 1161w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0507-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0507-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0507-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261447" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0515-488x580.jpg" alt="" width="488" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0515-488x580.jpg 488w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0515-scaled.jpg 757w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 488px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261445" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0564-477x580.jpg" alt="" width="477" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0564-477x580.jpg 477w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0564-741x900.jpg 741w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0564-scaled.jpg 740w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 477px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261453" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0565-694x465.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="465" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0565-694x465.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0565-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>開盒後就會見到主體處於人型形態，但那隻紅色成形色的主色再加上啞面，實在有點兒比較膠的感覺，欠缺了韋基利那種質感。人形態的機體高度約為 16 釐米，與市面上其他 VF-19 改產品相比，Hi-METALR 的機體更為纖細。雖然在用料方面，關鍵關節使用了金屬材料，確保了機體的穩固性，零件的鋭度仍然相當不錯，整體視覺效果還算可以接受，不過與官相對比，實物就有點兒比下去了，都是那隻紅色的處理問題；另外金屬手臂亦嫌比較幼小，有點不太成比例的感覺。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261455" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/171143562782_1200-410x580.jpg" alt="" width="410" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/171143562782_1200-410x580.jpg 410w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/171143562782_1200.jpg 589w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 410px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC0514" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975261078/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975261078_548904a3f4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0514" width="713" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261448" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0526-694x457.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="457" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0526-694x457.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0526-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261449" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0527-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0527-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0527-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261450" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0528-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0528-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0528-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261451" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0529-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0529-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0529-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>人型形態的手本身是比較細小的，是用作變形時收納用，若不喜歡亦有提供 4 對造型掌可換。此外，盾牌也提供了兩種選擇，人形態專用的盾牌造型較為纖細，而變形時使用的方形盾牌則更為方正。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1261452" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0566-694x362.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="362" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0566-694x362.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/dsc0566-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>至於變形方面，這款 VF-19 改的變形結構設計簡單且經過多年市場驗證，結構穩固，變形過程也相當順手。由於 Hi-METALR 系列體積較小，重量也較為輕量，操作起來會更為方便。不過，機體體積的縮小也導致部分功能有所削減，例如起落架和駕駛艙門的開合功能需要使用替換件來實現了。</p><p><a title="_DSC0534" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975346759/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975346759_831433e43a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0534" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0563" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975457890/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975457890_2e61894e2c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0563" width="1024" height="513" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>FIGHTER 形態</h2><p><a title="_DSC0560" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975260938/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975260938_55c45d66dc_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0560" width="1024" height="508" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0550" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975457915/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975457915_b219c6e4ce_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0550" width="1024" height="717" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC0551" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53974137907/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53974137907_3218fe1d1d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0551" width="1024" height="750" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0558" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975346744/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975346744_174f03bbbd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0558" width="1024" height="997" /></a></p><h2>GERWALK 形態</h2><p><a title="_DSC0546" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975028636/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975028636_96a67d5646_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0546" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0544" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53974137917/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53974137917_dbc1d4b200_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0544" width="1024" height="675" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0536" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975028676/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975028676_658d227958_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0536" width="1024" height="639" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>BATTROID 形態</h2><p><a title="_DSC0524" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975346804/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975346804_2e237436c3_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0524" width="812" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0521" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53975457970/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53975457970_7c15435f89_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0521" width="934" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>這款 Hi-METALR VF-19 改亦可當作為另一廠方 A 社或 Y 社的 VF-19 改縮小版，無論是變形結構設計還是外觀，都是十分相似。如果你覺得他廠的價格過高或者太大隻沒有空間擺放，選擇 Hi-METALR 作為替代品也是不錯的選擇。當然如果你對於《超時空要塞 7》有愛的話，相信這部 VF-19 改也應當可以吸引到你入手。</p><p><strong>HI-METAL R VF-19 改</strong><br />
參考售價：14,300 日圓（含稅）<br />
查詢：瑞華行</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/07/%e3%80%90%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac%e3%80%91bandai-hi-metal-r-%e8%b6%85%e6%99%82%e7%a9%ba%e8%a6%81%e5%a1%9e-macross-7-vf-19%e6%94%b9%e3%80%80%e6%9b%b4%e5%b0%8f%e6%af%94%e4%be%8b%e5%ae%8c%e5%85%a8%e8%ae%8a/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【評測】Bandai Hi-Metal R 超時空要塞 Macross 7 VF-19 改　更小比例完全變形</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
